    <h3>What is Treex?</h3>
    <p>Treex (formerly TectoMT) is a highly modular NLP software
    system implemented in Perl programming language under Linux.</p>
    <p>It is primarily aimed at Machine Translation, making use of the
    ideas and technology created during the Prague Dependency Treebank
    project. At the same time, it is also hoped to significantly
    facilitate and accelerate development of software solutions of
    many other NLP tasks, especially due to re-usability of the
    numerous integrated processing modules (called blocks), which are
    equipped with uniform object-oriented interfaces.
    </p>
